<title>ʿly̱ bạby</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- lạ tʿwd tqrʿ yạrby ʿly̱ bạby
 hạ ạ̉nạ ạ̉ftḥ ạ̉nạ ạ̉ftḥ qlby ltdkẖl yạrby wlttʿsẖy̱ mʿy
 1- ạ̉ḥbbtny rby ḥty̱ ạ̹ly̱ ạlṣlb
