 lyfdy mn ʿṣạk yṣlb mʿ ạlkẖṭạẗ
 fy ạljljtẖẗ hnạk whạ ạ̉nt wạqf
 ʿly̱ ạlbạb tqrʿ
 2- ṭlbtk rby bkl ạ̹rdạty
 rfḍtk rby lạ̉ʿln dẖạty
 bdẖnby ạ̉ṭʿn jnbk
 ạ̉smr qdmyk ạ̉dmy jbynk
 wạ̉tẖqb ydyk whạ ạ̉nt wạqf
 ʿly̱ ạlbạb tqrʿ
 3- ḍllt fy drby tht mʿ fkry
 trkt byt ạ̉by fḥrt fy ạ̉mry
 wbʿd kl dẖạ tqblny whạ tḍmny
 ḥlẗ tlbsny tfrḥ bʿwdty
 whạ ạ̉nt wạqf ʿly̱ ạlbạb tqrʿ</lyrics>
